\vspace{0.4cm}
\noindent \textbf{Weekly Goals \& Habits:}
\begin{itemize}
    \item \textbf{Positive Habit:} Nightly Review and Planning session on Sundays at 21:00.
    \item \textbf{Digital Usage:} Strict limit from 21:00 daily to ensure 8 hours of sleep hygiene.
    \item \textbf{Relaxation:} Meditation integrated into morning yoga and specific evening slots for music/prayer.
\end{itemize}

